@startuml
title Alarm Clock State Machine

[*] --> Off

state Activated
Activated : entry / Alarm activated
Activated : do / Alarm ringing
Activated : exit / Alarm stopped
Activated --> [*]

state Stopped
Stopped : entry / Alarm stopped
Stopped : do / Alarm remains active for next scheduled alarm time
Stopped : exit / Alarm activated
Stopped --> [*]

Off --> Activated : set alarm time

Activated --> Stopped : stop alarm

Stopped --> Activated : next scheduled alarm time

@enduml
